thread.title: Marino Cattapan
thread.title_full: Store DJ reviewed by Marino Cattapan

author: Marino Cattapan
title: Marino Cattapan
text:
I don't buy a lot of sound equipment but when I do it needs to available to me at short notice, usually with some advice as it needs to replace stuff we use which has been sourced or brought in from OS and, as always, at a reasonable price.
The crew at StoreDJ always step up to tick all the boxes.
I can thoroughly recommend them, especially the Richmond store crew.
